    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers a solid, dependable driving experience for someone looking for a practical car at a reasonable price. The exterior shows some clear signs of age, including noticeable scratches, a few small dents, and some fading in the paint on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few minor stains, but the cabin remains functional and comfortable. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been regularly serviced, though it may soon require attention to standard wear-and-tear items like brake pads or tires. It\u2019s a reliable choice for a daily commuter or a first car, provided you don't mind a bit of cosmetic character.",
