    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride, and she's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and still looks great on the road. I've taken great care of it, so it's ready to hit the pavement with a new owner today. It's the perfect balance of comfort and dependability without the 'brand new' price tag. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual VANOS for linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-spec variable M differential lock, the mechanical feedback is tactile and precise. The chassis remains taut with documented rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings. While the exterior shows minor stone chipping and interior patina consistent with spirited use, the powertrain remains robust with consistent compression across all cylinders and a recently serviced rod bearing kit. A visceral, analog machine engineered for the enthusiast.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Ready for immediate sale.",
