    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-cared-for driver. The exterior paint retains a deep, glossy finish with only minor, negligible road wear consistent with careful ownership. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the premium upholstery is free of cracks or stains, and the dashboard remains pristine. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the high-fidelity sound system, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule. It has recently undergone a full fluid flush and a comprehensive safety inspection, ensuring it is ready for the road the moment you turn the key. This is a smoke-free, garage-kept car that offers a refined driving experience and a solid service history.",
      "price": 34500.0,
