      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left for all your weekend adventures or daily commutes. It\u2019s super reliable and ready to hit the road whenever you are! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great new home!",
