    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system. This example utilizes the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, providing tactile engagement and precise gear selection. The chassis remains composed thanks to a reinforced rear subframe and a factory-spec limited-slip differential that ensures optimal power delivery through the corners. Maintenance has been prioritized, with recent valve clearances performed and a cooling system overhaul to manage thermal loads during spirited driving. While the aesthetics show minor signs of use, the drivetrain is robust, offering the raw, analog feedback that defines this generation of M-car.",
